================================================================================
libquiv-aging — Python port of Mmeka–Dubarry–Bessler (2025) aging model
================================================================================

This work is a Python port of the MATLAB implementation accompanying:

  Mmeka P. O., Dubarry M., Bessler W. G.
  "Physics-Informed Aging-Sensitive Equivalent Circuit Model for
   Predicting the Knee in Lithium-Ion Batteries"
  Journal of The Electrochemical Society, 172, 080538 (2025)
  DOI: 10.1149/1945-7111/adf9cb

